column5: On our way home from a visit up at pop and mudders,I was sadden  to see the big sign  EVERYTHING MUST GO,RETIRING.  Really enjoyed stopping into thier shop and browse.Another one of those childhood memories that will last for ever and be a ,remember when..  Enjoy your retirement.You done a great job.
Yes .. kinda sad .. they were the only stop between Waubaushene and Mactier on the Muskoka route
